  "text": "The FiberCup phantom was built based on the procedure introduced in [CITATION_1] and it was used in the MICCAI 2009 tractography challenge [CITATION_2] . The data is extensively studied and tested in several tractography papers for benchmarking purposes [CITATION_3] . The dMRI data for the FiberCup can be freely downloaded from http://www.tractometer.org/original_fibercup/data/. In our tests we used the average data with b-value 1500.",
